5
00:00:18.690 --> 00:00:19.440
One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece One Piece

6
00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:48.210
Queen vs. Olin

7
00:01:53.530 --> 00:01:56.580
Oshiruko...

8
00:02:02.730 --> 00:02:04.190
Olin?!

9
00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:09.610
Olin hasn't lost an ounce of strength
from when she was Big Mom!

10
00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.350
Luffy!

11
00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:27.710
What a formidable old lady!

12
00:02:28.320 --> 00:02:31.240
She's not just any "old lady."

13
00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:32.420
She's...

14
00:02:37.950 --> 00:02:39.450
one of the Four Emperors!

15
00:02:41.220 --> 00:02:42.890
Wait... what?!

16
00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:01.770
Queen, Your Awesomeness!

17
00:03:05.100 --> 00:03:05.890
Hey.

18
00:03:06.730 --> 00:03:10.900
Quit lying around, you damn lizard!

19
00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:18.680
Stop it already, you old bag!

20
00:03:18.700 --> 00:03:21.560
Just who do you think I am?!

21
00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:30.190
Luffy!

22
00:03:36.070 --> 00:03:43.810
Oshiruko!

23
00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:51.000
Give me my oshiruko!

24
00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:53.560
Oshiruko!

25
00:03:54.380 --> 00:03:57.610
Oshiruko!

26
00:03:58.200 --> 00:04:01.930
Give it to me already!

27
00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:13.630
Get down, gramps!

28
00:04:37.030 --> 00:04:38.880
U-Udon...

29
00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:42.120
Udon's in danger!

30
00:05:01.430 --> 00:05:03.760
Good, those two...

31
00:05:03.760 --> 00:05:05.160
Hey, are you okay?!

32
00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:22.110
Your Awesomeness!

33
00:05:22.110 --> 00:05:24.580
Your Awesomeness! Stay with us!

34
00:05:25.740 --> 00:05:26.640
Your Awesomeness?

35
00:05:27.410 --> 00:05:30.600
He passed out...

36
00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:35.400
A man with a 1.3-billion-berry bounty
was K.O.'d in just two hits!

37
00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:44.410
That sweet red-bean aroma is getting stronger!

38
00:05:44.850 --> 00:05:47.850
She took down Queen
without breaking a sweat.

39
00:05:48.810 --> 00:05:51.310
She's on another level...

40
00:05:51.310 --> 00:05:53.960
So that's Emperor Big Mom?!

41
00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:59.820
We must report to Lord Kaido!

42
00:05:58.400 --> 00:05:59.820
Roger!

43
00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:05.660
The unopened cell is a wreck!

44
00:06:05.660 --> 00:06:08.540
I don't know what's inside...

45
00:06:08.540 --> 00:06:10.950
I believe it was chained up...

46
00:06:10.950 --> 00:06:15.170
It couldn't escape,
so there's no way it's still alive.

47
00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:22.490
Executive
Tower


Prisoner
Mining
Camp

48
00:06:22.490 --> 00:06:26.870
Understood. I'll inform
Onigashima immediately.

49
00:06:40.280 --> 00:06:43.840
It smells like oshiruko over here.

50
00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:48.030
Babanuki, requesting permission to fire.

51
00:06:48.030 --> 00:06:51.240
Denied! Don't agitate her!

52
00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.480
What are Lord Kaido's orders?

53
00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:54.710
Warden, the smails...

54
00:06:54.710 --> 00:06:58.090
The smails aren't connecting!

55
00:06:58.090 --> 00:07:00.690
None of us can reach Onigashima!

56
00:07:02.460 --> 00:07:03.780
What the hell?!

57
00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:12.140
Their guard is down
thanks to the commotion out front.

58
00:07:12.140 --> 00:07:14.750
Caribou has also played a role.

59
00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:23.940
Basically, it's all, "He went that way,"
or, "He's over here."

60
00:07:23.940 --> 00:07:27.860
Their constant communication is a real pain!

61
00:07:27.860 --> 00:07:32.700
Now, let me tell you the important thing.

62
00:07:34.870 --> 00:07:35.690
You see...

63
00:07:35.690 --> 00:07:41.150
Smart

Snail

(abbr. "Smail")

64
00:07:35.710 --> 00:07:41.150
Wano's smart snails are at a disadvantage
due to their weak signals!

65
00:07:41.150 --> 00:07:56.120
Boss Snail

66
00:07:41.670 --> 00:07:45.340
To compensate,
every Smail's outgoing signal...

67
00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:50.890
is first sent to what's called a boss snail
that's set up in every region...

68
00:07:50.890 --> 00:07:56.120
The boss snail then relays
the signal to the receiving smails.

69
00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:59.440
Huh? I understand how
the system works, but...

70
00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:02.820
Come on, don't be dense!

71
00:08:02.820 --> 00:08:08.880
If I were to slurp up Udon's boss snail...

72
00:08:10.410 --> 00:08:12.760
what do you think might happen?

73
00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:18.370
Do you mean to say the entire
Udon region would be cut off?!

74
00:08:18.370 --> 00:08:20.650
That's exactly right!

75
00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:27.280
I wasn't locked in here for so long for nothing.

76
00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:33.600
I already know where the boss snail is.

77
00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:35.540
Truly?!

78
00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:43.480
You can just leave cutting
their communications to me!

79
00:08:43.570 --> 00:08:50.220
The keys are the key to our plan,
so go snatch 'em all up, my dear Raizo!

80
00:08:51.570 --> 00:08:52.930
Hang on, Kawamatsu!

81
00:08:53.530 --> 00:08:56.790
We will set you free at any cost!

82
00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:00.170
Huh?

83
00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:07.010
Here it is!

84
00:09:07.010 --> 00:09:09.380
That aroma!

85
00:09:09.380 --> 00:09:10.930
No doubt!

86
00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:14.530
It's oshiruko!

87
00:09:16.430 --> 00:09:19.350
What a sweet, rich aroma!

88
00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:22.650
And look at how much there is!

89
00:09:23.770 --> 00:09:27.860
It was well worth the trip!

90
00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.260
Now, let's see.

91
00:09:30.650 --> 00:09:31.590
Warden Babanuki!

92
00:09:31.590 --> 00:09:34.780
I have an urgent matter to report!

93
00:09:34.780 --> 00:09:36.790
What? Can't it wait?!

94
00:09:36.790 --> 00:09:39.810
That oshiruko pot is empty!

95
00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:43.790
It's empty?!

96
00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:49.300
With her food obsession,
what will Big Mom do

97
00:09:49.300 --> 00:09:51.860
when she finds out the oshiruko is gone?!

98
00:09:51.860 --> 00:09:56.990
Where will she direct her rage?!
We're probably all dead men walking!

99
00:09:59.850 --> 00:10:02.500
Oshiruko.

100
00:10:18.100 --> 00:10:20.310
Everyone, evacuate immediately!

101
00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:23.520
Save yourselves!

102
00:10:23.540 --> 00:10:27.770
An unpredictable disaster is upon us!

103
00:10:30.070 --> 00:10:33.650
Shit! Who the hell ate it all?!

104
00:10:37.180 --> 00:10:40.660
Makes sense. She really wanted to eat some.

105
00:10:40.660 --> 00:10:46.000
I get how she feels.
I'd love to have some more.

106
00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:49.380
That oshiruko sure tasted good!

107
00:10:55.890 --> 00:10:57.340
Sir Straw Hat!

108
00:11:01.770 --> 00:11:02.450
So...

109
00:11:02.450 --> 00:11:03.660
– So... So...
– So... So...

110
00:11:03.660 --> 00:11:05.480
So you're the one...

111
00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:08.690
– ...who ate it!
– ...who ate it!

112
00:11:08.710 --> 00:11:11.500
Why's everyone looking at me?

113
00:11:11.500 --> 00:11:13.610
W-Wait, what? You just...

114
00:11:14.220 --> 00:11:17.260
announced to everyone
that you ate the oshiruko.

115
00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:18.320
What?!

116
00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:20.310
I said that out loud?!

117
00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:22.850
I thought, "The oshiruko sure was good,"

118
00:11:22.850 --> 00:11:25.410
but I didn't mean to say it!

119
00:11:25.410 --> 00:11:28.690
You just said it again. Are you okay?

120
00:11:28.690 --> 00:11:30.090
Luffytaro...

121
00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:34.570
I finally found you, Luffy...

122
00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:38.390
but once again, you're the center of trouble!

123
00:11:40.910 --> 00:11:41.970
Hey...!

124
00:11:43.540 --> 00:11:46.080
Did you...

125
00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:51.440
eat all the oshiruko?!

126
00:11:57.180 --> 00:12:01.030
You smell like oshiruko!

127
00:12:01.030 --> 00:12:02.660
Oh no!

128
00:12:03.770 --> 00:12:06.940
Oshiruko!

129
00:12:25.290 --> 00:12:27.960
Th... Th-That was close!

130
00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:31.540
I gotta remember that we'll die
if we go outside the ring!

131
00:12:31.540 --> 00:12:33.440
I won't stand for this.

132
00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.110
W-Wait a sec!

133
00:12:35.110 --> 00:12:37.740
You gotta hear me out! Wait, Big Mom!

134
00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:40.950
Who the hell is this "Big Mom"?!

135
00:12:41.530 --> 00:12:43.870
Who the hell are you talking about?!

136
00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:49.310
and who the hell are you, red-bean eater?!

137
00:12:50.900 --> 00:12:51.880
What?!

138
00:12:53.230 --> 00:12:55.750
You don't remember me?!

139
00:12:55.750 --> 00:13:00.510
Oh! I'm dressed as a samurai,
so you don't recognize me!

140
00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:05.510
Making Big Mom angry
over food brings disaster...

141
00:13:12.920 --> 00:13:14.980
This is bad! Really bad!

142
00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:23.530
The collar started ticking again!

143
00:13:24.260 --> 00:13:25.830
This is not good.

144
00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:29.520
One more push and we're dead!

145
00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:32.120
We cannot yield even an inch!

146
00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:37.460
If that pot were full of oshiruko,

147
00:13:37.460 --> 00:13:42.260
I could have shared it with
everyone from that town!

148
00:13:42.990 --> 00:13:46.600
Have some oshiruko. Go ahead, Olin!

149
00:13:48.850 --> 00:13:55.020
Everyone in that poor town
was so kind to me...

150
00:13:55.230 --> 00:14:00.190
I wanted to show my gratitude
by bringing them a lot of oshiruko!

151
00:14:00.190 --> 00:14:01.280
What?!

152
00:14:02.430 --> 00:14:05.760
That yummy oshiruko...

153
00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:10.370
I wanted to share it with them!

154
00:14:10.370 --> 00:14:13.100
Th-Th-Th...

155
00:14:13.100 --> 00:14:16.130
So this isn't one of her Ravenous Rampages?

156
00:14:16.860 --> 00:14:19.050
She's acting out of kindness?!

157
00:14:19.730 --> 00:14:23.780
She went on a rampage
because she wanted to be nice!

158
00:14:23.780 --> 00:14:26.830
Oshiruko!

159
00:14:26.830 --> 00:14:29.390
Why'd you eat it all?!

160
00:14:29.390 --> 00:14:32.020
You little brat!

161
00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:33.940
No, stop!

162
00:14:41.690 --> 00:14:42.630
Gramps!

163
00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:47.870
Come off!

164
00:14:47.890 --> 00:14:51.450
Dammit! I won't let you die! You can't die!

165
00:14:51.450 --> 00:14:52.930
Come off!

166
00:14:53.410 --> 00:14:55.980
Come off!

167
00:15:01.280 --> 00:15:03.950
So this is it...?

168
00:15:04.820 --> 00:15:07.800
Come off!

169
00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:16.210
Come... off!

170
00:15:34.410 --> 00:15:36.290
Ah, the collars!

171
00:15:46.490 --> 00:15:47.180
What?

172
00:15:51.160 --> 00:15:52.790
The collars came off!

173
00:15:52.790 --> 00:15:55.410
What'd I do, gramps?!

174
00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:57.710
I did it!

175
00:15:58.900 --> 00:16:01.690
Well, I'll be damned. That was...

176
00:15:58.900 --> 00:16:00.750
It came off!

177
00:16:04.050 --> 00:16:06.400
You dodged me again.

178
00:16:06.400 --> 00:16:09.260
Alright, let's get outta here, gramps!

179
00:16:09.260 --> 00:16:10.570
Sir Straw Hat!

180
00:16:11.950 --> 00:16:15.480
Before you forget the sensation,

181
00:16:15.480 --> 00:16:17.790
use it to protect me!

182
00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:20.460
What the hell are you saying?! Let's move!

183
00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:23.590
Power blooms in our darkest hour!

184
00:16:23.610 --> 00:16:25.800
You won't get away this time!

185
00:16:25.820 --> 00:16:28.280
Are you crazy?! We're training now?!

186
00:16:28.280 --> 00:16:31.820
If I fail, you're dead!

187
00:16:32.680 --> 00:16:34.140
I know!

188
00:16:39.750 --> 00:16:42.520
Come at me, Emperor!

189
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:47.550
I can do it too! Just like
Rayleigh did in Sabaody!

190
00:16:58.020 --> 00:17:01.650
I'm going to remove your collar now.
Would that be okay, young lady?

191
00:17:02.790 --> 00:17:06.990
Don't be rash, grandpa! It'll explode!

192
00:17:06.990 --> 00:17:10.510
We saw one of
the slave collars explode earlier!

193
00:17:10.530 --> 00:17:13.260
That's a bad idea! A very bad idea!

194
00:17:13.260 --> 00:17:14.510
Is this okay, Luffy?!

195
00:17:17.120 --> 00:17:20.350
It'll be all right. Just stay still.

196
00:17:23.020 --> 00:17:27.360
I'm telling you it's too dangerous!
It won't come off without the key!

197
00:17:35.720 --> 00:17:39.500
It's ticking! What're we gonna do?!

198
00:17:44.420 --> 00:17:46.300
Stop! Please stop already!

199
00:17:49.900 --> 00:17:53.050
Camie!

200
00:18:00.540 --> 00:18:02.100
He removed the collar bare-handed?!

201
00:18:07.380 --> 00:18:08.690
That's right.

202
00:18:08.690 --> 00:18:12.530
It was exactly the same as
what Rayleigh did back then!

203
00:18:13.470 --> 00:18:15.620
I just did it too!

204
00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:20.200
But I was so desperate.
I don't remember how I did it at all!

205
00:18:21.810 --> 00:18:23.850
You're mine now!

206
00:18:25.900 --> 00:18:30.710
Sir Straw Hat, the ability
you manifested just now

207
00:18:30.710 --> 00:18:35.200
already far surpasses anything
I can teach you about ryuo.

208
00:18:35.660 --> 00:18:38.640
So I'm sure you can stop her!

209
00:18:39.040 --> 00:18:42.100
Repel that monstrous woman's fists

210
00:18:42.560 --> 00:18:45.710
and save us both!

211
00:18:46.380 --> 00:18:48.380
I know you can do it!

212
00:18:48.380 --> 00:18:53.130
Alright, show me what you've got!

213
00:18:55.390 --> 00:18:56.780
You're ready to die?!

214
00:18:57.300 --> 00:18:58.330
Absolutely!

215
00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:00.490
Alright!

216
00:19:00.490 --> 00:19:03.890
He can't intend to block that!
It'd be so reckless!

217
00:19:03.890 --> 00:19:04.790
No...

218
00:19:04.790 --> 00:19:07.130
I'm sure Luffy can do it.

219
00:19:08.590 --> 00:19:13.300
I don't need to strain.
I just channel haki into my fists.

220
00:19:13.860 --> 00:19:14.930
Bring it on!

221
00:19:33.170 --> 00:19:34.800
Luffytaro!

222
00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:37.820
Luffy!

223
00:19:44.140 --> 00:19:46.750
Luffy!

224
00:19:46.770 --> 00:19:50.210
– What the hell did you expect?!
– What the hell did you expect?!

225
00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:56.990
Dammit!

226
00:20:01.530 --> 00:20:04.250
Sorry, gramps! I failed!

227
00:20:04.250 --> 00:20:06.790
Don't die on me!

228
00:20:09.190 --> 00:20:11.210
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

229
00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.070
Are you okay, gramps?!

230
00:20:15.300 --> 00:20:20.120
I-I somewhat protected myself with ryuo...

231
00:20:20.140 --> 00:20:21.280
Gramps!

232
00:20:23.850 --> 00:20:26.330
You're still alive?!

233
00:20:30.310 --> 00:20:31.880
Listen to me...

234
00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:38.280
All I can teach you...

235
00:20:38.280 --> 00:20:41.700
is the technique to coat your body in ryuo...

236
00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:44.160
What you call haki–

237
00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:45.600
Hey, don't speak.

238
00:20:48.460 --> 00:20:49.900
Haki is...

239
00:20:49.900 --> 00:20:56.960
a powerful force that is both
an invisible armor and a tool for offense.

240
00:20:59.880 --> 00:21:03.100
However, advance to the next level,

241
00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:06.410
the haki that covers you
will become even stronger,

242
00:21:06.410 --> 00:21:12.560
reaching inside your opponents
and destroying them from within.

243
00:21:14.610 --> 00:21:23.200
You destroyed those steel collars
from within, using your haki.

244
00:21:26.160 --> 00:21:28.890
You have already done it.

245
00:21:30.750 --> 00:21:31.980
Gramps...

246
00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:37.960
You've already mastered
sheathing your body in haki.

247
00:21:40.680 --> 00:21:42.720
You just don't realize it yet...

248
00:21:45.450 --> 00:21:49.100
Believe in your abilities!

249
00:22:17.690 --> 00:22:19.940
Hey, gramps!

250
00:22:19.940 --> 00:22:22.110
Don't die on me, gramps!

251
00:22:22.110 --> 00:22:26.180
Hey! Stay with me, gramps!

252
00:22:27.990 --> 00:22:29.660
Hey! Don't die on me!

253
00:22:29.660 --> 00:22:30.750
Hey!

254
00:22:30.770 --> 00:22:34.230
Gramps!

255
00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:42.300
How dare you eat the oshiruko that was
meant for me and everyone else!

256
00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:48.680
I'll never forgive you!

257
00:22:53.440 --> 00:22:56.520
Good luck, Sir Straw Hat!

258
00:22:56.540 --> 00:23:01.990
Prison
Ironworks

Udon

259
00:23:04.930 --> 00:23:07.720
Hey, there's no signal!

260
00:23:07.720 --> 00:23:11.390
I heard that the boss snail disappeared!

261
00:23:11.390 --> 00:23:12.200
What?!

262
00:23:24.240 --> 00:23:25.800
What's that rumbling?!

263
00:23:55.520 --> 00:23:57.980
– B-Big Mom?!
– B-Big Mom?!

264
00:23:59.980 --> 00:24:01.520
Hold it!

265
00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:12.410
The furnace in the prison
ironworks has blown up!

266
00:24:12.410 --> 00:24:16.230
What am I supposed to do?
After all, Big Mom's an Emperor!

267
00:24:24.380 --> 00:24:29.820
Even His Awesomeness couldn't match her.
What hope would we have against her...?!

268
00:24:36.910 --> 00:24:39.080
Y-Your Awesomeness!

269
00:24:39.080 --> 00:24:42.270
Wano is Lord Kaido's territory.

270
00:24:42.270 --> 00:24:45.610
We can't let that old bag do as she pleases!

271
00:24:48.990 --> 00:24:51.720
Hold it!

272
00:25:02.860 --> 00:25:05.030
I've got an idea.

273
00:25:05.030 --> 00:25:08.400
We've got only one chance. Listen up!

274
00:25:12.410 --> 00:25:15.780
You're mine, you little brat!

275
00:25:26.500 --> 00:25:30.430
You see, Big Mom is like a wild boar!

276
00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:44.560
She'll charge forward around Udon
and loop right back here.

277
00:25:44.560 --> 00:25:46.860
So, we'll set a trap!

278
00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:52.360
Damn you!

279
00:25:52.360 --> 00:25:54.700
Take this!

280
00:26:13.090 --> 00:26:13.920
Oshiruko

281
00:26:21.600 --> 00:26:25.150
Your Awesomeness, everything's ready!

282
00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:37.530
She's here, Your Awesomeness!

283
00:26:46.250 --> 00:26:48.750
Damn! She's so persistent!

284
00:26:48.750 --> 00:26:51.210
Hold it!

285
00:27:03.310 --> 00:27:05.770
Oshiruko!

286
00:27:06.690 --> 00:27:09.690
Oshiruko!

287
00:27:12.110 --> 00:27:13.650
Yes, it worked!

288
00:27:14.990 --> 00:27:16.280
Hooray!

289
00:27:22.370 --> 00:27:23.450
It's empty!

290
00:27:26.120 --> 00:27:29.460
Did you eat it all again?!

291
00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:32.380
You bastard!

292
00:27:32.380 --> 00:27:34.760
No, it wasn't me this time!

293
00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:37.430
Brachio...

294
00:27:39.350 --> 00:27:41.140
Bomber!

295
00:27:58.160 --> 00:28:00.910
It worked! He got her!

296
00:28:00.910 --> 00:28:03.370
All hail His Awesomeness Queen!

297
00:28:03.370 --> 00:28:05.370
His Awesomeness is being true to form!

298
00:28:05.370 --> 00:28:07.830
He's the savior of Wano!

299
00:28:12.130 --> 00:28:13.920
Mama...!

300
00:28:13.920 --> 00:28:15.130
Mama...

301
00:28:15.130 --> 00:28:16.340
Mama!

302
00:28:17.720 --> 00:28:21.760
My adorable children...

303
00:28:21.760 --> 00:28:24.270
Huh? My head hurts.

304
00:28:25.430 --> 00:28:29.230
What was I doing?

305
00:28:29.230 --> 00:28:30.770
That's right!

306
00:28:32.270 --> 00:28:37.610
I traveled all the way
to Wano to kill Straw Hat...

307
00:28:37.610 --> 00:28:42.620
when that bastard King
kicked me into the sea.

308
00:28:43.450 --> 00:28:45.700
I washed up on the shore...

309
00:28:47.250 --> 00:28:50.670
went to a dirty little town...

310
00:28:50.670 --> 00:28:55.460
and ate some oshiruko.

311
00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:04.430
Don't mess with a Superstar!

312
00:29:06.470 --> 00:29:09.480
Damn, you sure gave me a lot of trouble.

313
00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:12.900
Stop screwing with me, you old bag!

314
00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:18.070
Oshiruko.

315
00:29:20.490 --> 00:29:23.410
Oh no... This is bad! This is really bad!

316
00:29:23.410 --> 00:29:25.870
What's wrong, Chopperemon?

317
00:29:26.370 --> 00:29:29.040
H-Hey... You gotta be kidding me...

318
00:29:29.040 --> 00:29:31.330
My attack had absolutely no effect?

319
00:29:32.540 --> 00:29:34.040
Oh?

320
00:29:34.670 --> 00:29:39.130
You're one of Kaido's boys... Queen, right?

321
00:29:39.130 --> 00:29:41.010
I'm done for!

322
00:29:41.010 --> 00:29:43.220
No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no...!

323
00:29:43.220 --> 00:29:46.560
This monster is nothing like she was before!

324
00:29:48.100 --> 00:29:50.850
Anyway, I heard...

325
00:29:50.850 --> 00:29:55.020
you've got some oshiruko, right?

326
00:29:55.020 --> 00:29:57.780
Just hand it over.

327
00:30:00.650 --> 00:30:03.780
Oshiruko... Oshiruko...

328
00:30:04.870 --> 00:30:06.740
What happened to her?

329
00:30:09.290 --> 00:30:12.370
Give me some oshiruko!

330
00:30:17.000 --> 00:30:19.300
I-I'm dead meat.

331
00:30:38.230 --> 00:30:40.070
Men!

332
00:30:40.070 --> 00:30:45.160
Bring me 100-percent-pure
seastone cuffs and chains!

333
00:30:45.160 --> 00:30:46.820
Hurry!

334
00:30:46.820 --> 00:30:48.120
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

335
00:30:51.620 --> 00:30:54.120
Wrap these around her 100 times!

336
00:30:54.120 --> 00:30:55.580
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

337
00:31:01.300 --> 00:31:03.800
Job's done, sir!

338
00:31:02.720 --> 00:31:03.800
Alright!

339
00:31:03.800 --> 00:31:08.470
That's not enough! We need more!
I still don't feel safe!

340
00:31:08.470 --> 00:31:10.430
We gotta do more!

341
00:31:10.430 --> 00:31:13.430
Give her 100 wild animal tranquilizers!

342
00:31:13.430 --> 00:31:14.850
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

343
00:31:17.190 --> 00:31:20.230
Alright! Is the ship ready to go?!

344
00:31:20.230 --> 00:31:22.280
Yes, sir! It's ready to go!

345
00:31:22.280 --> 00:31:26.200
Then leave this place minimally manned

346
00:31:26.200 --> 00:31:28.240
while the rest of us board the ship!

347
00:31:28.240 --> 00:31:32.200
Babanuki, I'm leaving Udon
wholly under your charge!

348
00:31:32.200 --> 00:31:33.700
Y-Yes, sir!

349
00:31:33.700 --> 00:31:37.790
That old bag busted just about
every door in Udon!

350
00:31:37.790 --> 00:31:43.010
So once I'm gone, lock down Udon
with the emergency gates!

351
00:31:43.010 --> 00:31:46.970
Throw the prisoners in their cells
and get this place under control!

352
00:31:46.970 --> 00:31:49.260
Leave it to me! However, there is one man–

353
00:31:49.260 --> 00:31:51.140
Let's go!

354
00:31:54.680 --> 00:31:56.600
We're in a race against time!

355
00:31:56.600 --> 00:31:59.860
We gotta bring this old bag to Lord Kaido!

356
00:31:59.860 --> 00:32:01.690
Get a move on!

357
00:32:08.570 --> 00:32:10.070
Set sail!

358
00:32:10.620 --> 00:32:16.580
Full speed ahead! On to Onigashima!

359
00:32:19.920 --> 00:32:22.590
Momo, the gate's closing!

360
00:32:22.590 --> 00:32:26.470
There's nothing we can do.
We promised we'd wait here.

361
00:32:26.470 --> 00:32:29.220
We must trust the others and wait patiently.

362
00:32:31.260 --> 00:32:32.350
Let's go!

363
00:32:32.350 --> 00:32:34.060
Are all the gates sealed?!

364
00:32:34.060 --> 00:32:35.270
Yes, sir!

365
00:32:35.270 --> 00:32:37.020
Have we reopened the comms?!

366
00:32:37.020 --> 00:32:39.230
No, not yet!

367
00:32:39.230 --> 00:32:42.690
Udon is still completely isolated!

368
00:32:42.690 --> 00:32:45.530
We have no way at all to contact
anywhere outside Udon!

369
00:32:45.530 --> 00:32:46.570
What the hell?!

370
00:32:47.950 --> 00:32:50.990
In that case, I'm free to go wild.

371
00:32:54.910 --> 00:32:58.620
This'll be a cinch without Big Mom
or that balloon here, though.

372
00:32:59.290 --> 00:33:01.830
I guess it's time to continue my training.

373
00:33:01.830 --> 00:33:04.840
That's right. This punk was still free.

374
00:33:08.170 --> 00:33:10.220
Oh, but...

375
00:33:10.220 --> 00:33:12.390
I've always been free!

376
00:33:13.140 --> 00:33:16.600
Prisoners should know not to push their luck.

377
00:33:17.020 --> 00:33:19.020
I hate to break it to you,

378
00:33:19.020 --> 00:33:20.900
but I'm gonna take over Udon!
